    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday reliability. The exterior boasts a vibrant, well-preserved finish that catches the light beautifully, with only minor, negligible imperfections consistent with careful use. Inside, you'll find a pristine, smoke-free interior featuring premium upholstery that remains firm and comfortable. All electronics, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, function exactly as they should. Under the hood, the car has been treated with respect; it starts promptly, idles quietly, and delivers smooth power through every gear. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change, new air filters, and a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it is road-ready. This is a dependable, sharp-looking car that offers a high-quality driving experience for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
