      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty car and it\u2019s been such a gem to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014honestly, it still runs like a dream! It\u2019s been well-loved and looked after, making it the perfect ride for someone who wants a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. I'd love for it to go to a great new home, so come by and take it for a spin!",
