      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This example boasts critical preventative maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. The individual throttle bodies provide instantaneous throttle response, while the factory M-Variable limited-slip differential ensures optimal power delivery through the corners. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and a well-sorted suspension geometry. A mechanically robust specimen for the purist seeking analog feedback and a 8,000 RPM redline.",
